CustomField.description: Dynamic lookups do not have a defined metadata pull configurations from. This field used to identify which dynamic lookups to configure. The format is <sObjectAPIName>-<fieldAPIName>. Exmaple: "ucinn_ascendv2__Contact_Report__c-ucinn_ascendv2__Contact__c".
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Enable configurations for defined dynamic lookup. String of object API name and field API name separated by hyphen. Exmaple: "ucinn_ascendv2__Contact_Report__c-ucinn_ascendv2__Contact__c".
CustomField.label: Dynamic Lookup to Configure
